desc: Place your iPhone quickly and easily with one hand movement in a stand that keeps your dashboard free of adapters and cables. A nice cradle for only one tenth of the price compared to its direct competitors. Specially made for Audi, BMW, Land Rover, Jaguar cup holders.

layout.text: Smart iPhone Mount for Car Cup Holder
The perfect solution to quickly connect your phone to the Audi, Jaguar, BMW, Land Rover, Jeep, and KIA Apple CarPlay
